mpservice
=========

A media-player service with integrated media database, web-server, and 
web-services control interface.  mpservice is primarily intended to be used 
with the mpbox embedded Linux platform, but can also run as a standalone
Linux application.

Instructions to build with mpbox:
  (Clone the mpbox project and follow it's README)

Instructions to build standalone:
  % source x86-glibc-linux-standalone.env
  % make download
  % make standalone

